title: Midseason CFB Report Card
description:
Wendi Nix, Roddy Jones, and David Pollack give their midseason report cards for all the Power 5 teams. Also, Jay Walker joins the show to give his updated HBCU Power Rankings. Plus, Todd McShay gives his take on which NFL prospects are rising and falling halfway through the season. Then, how are the newly hired head coaches faring so far into the 2022 season.
